reviewText:
Very good product, now my wife is really happy 
Good and fast seller, highly recommended

This is an older movie that was never made into DVD state.  I had one VHS copy and it was so bad.  I think it came from a movie store and watched over and over and over.  I bought this second one from Amazon and the quality is much better.  Still not as good as a DVD, but the best I can get seeing it is on available on VHS.
